The paper focuses on remote sensing image retrieval using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The proposed method involves the use of a convolutional neural network (CNN) and a hash layer, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Additionally, the paper involves classification of semantic labels, which is a task commonly associated with artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research.
